milestones.description: Lance Cairns has become the top wicket-taker for NZ in ODIs with 27 wickets, going past Hadlee's 26
Kapil Dev has broken the record for most sixes in an innings (3) in ODIs for IND, going past Brijesh Patel's 2
Kapil Dev has broken the record for most runs in boundaries (54) in an innings in ODIs for IND, going past Brijesh Patel's 44
Syed Kirmani has broken the record for most dismissals (5) in ODIs for IND, going past Engineer's 4
Vengsarkar has broken the record for most catches (5) in ODIs for IND, going past Bishan Bedi's 4
Kapil Dev and Sandeep Patil's 52-run partnership is IND's highest for the 6th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 40 between Gavaskar and Kapil Dev
